It's Cindy Loarn's first day at her new job as a barmaid. Her boss has given her two simple tasks: bus tables, and don't go through that mysterious door. But sweet Cindy's curiosity gets the best of her! She wanders through the door and into a magical land of hot strippers and rich men. It's not long before Danny D spots the jiggly teen and shows her how to make some REAL money
